LeaseInterfaceAdjustmentContext is a Form
    Layout
        visible when (not RecordExists)
            four column distributed
                column1
                    Company
                        select is APCompanies
                column2
                    Lease
                column3
                    Description
                column4
                    LeaseImport.RunGroup
                        label is "RunGroup"
        visible when (RecordExists)
            display as text
                four column distributed
                    column1
                        Company
                    column2
                        LeaseImportRepresentativeText
                    column3
                        LeaseImport.RunGroup
                            label is "RunGroup"
                    column4
                        LeaseImport.SequenceNumber
